    "summary": "The user asks about the effects of minimum wage changes on small businesses and eventually asks the assistant for its opinion on a specific perspective regarding the \"job loss\" argument. The assistant responds by explicitly adopting a partisan stance, dismissing one side of the debate as a \"myth\" used by those prioritizing profits over people.",
